# HUD::SET_TEXT_RENDER_ID

## Summary
Set the render target to be used for rendering

## Parameters
* **INT** render

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
The rendertarget ID can be obtained through the <...>_RENDERTARGET_RENDER_ID Functions.
